contents:
[[bench]]
name = "benchmarks"
harness = false

[package]
name = "audio-ops"
version = "1.0.0"
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]
once_cell = "1.18.0"
riff-wave = "0.1.3"

[dev-dependencies]
divan = "0.1.2"

[package]
name = "espeak-phonemizer"
version = "1.0.0"
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]
ffi-support = "0.4.4"
once_cell = "1.18.0"
regex = "1.9.3"

[build-dependencies]
autotools = "0.2.7"

[package]
name = "sonata-piper"
version = "0.2.0"
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]
ndarray = "0.15.6"
serde_json = "1.0.89"

[dependencies.espeak-phonemizer]
path = "../../../espeak-phonemizer"

[dependencies.sonata-core]
path = "../../core"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.160"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.libtashkeel_base]
version = "1.5.0"
default-features = false
features = [ "ort", "rayon",]

[dependencies.ort]
version = "2.0.0-rc.1"

[[bench]]
name = "benchmarks"
path = "src/benchmarks.rs"
harness = false

[[test]]
name = "tests"
path = "src/tests.rs"

[package]
name = "sonata-synth"
version = "0.2.0"
edition = "2021"

[lib]
name = "sonata_synth"

[dependencies]
rayon = "1.7.0"
once_cell = "1.18.0"

[dev-dependencies]
once_cell = "1.18.0"
divan = "0.1.2"

[dependencies.sonata-core]
path = "../core"

[dependencies.sonic-sys]
path = "../../sonic-sys"

[dependencies.audio-ops]
path = "../../audio-ops"

[dependencies.flume]
version = "0.11.0"
default-features = false
features = [ "async",]

[dev-dependencies.sonata-piper]
path = "../models/piper"

[dev-dependencies.ort]
version = "2.0.0-rc.1"

[package]
name = "sonic-sys"
version = "1.0.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Musharraf Omer <ibnomer2011@hotmail.com>",]
description = "Raw FFI bindings to sonic rate boost library"
license = "MIT"
keywords = [ "FFI", "sonic", "audio", "tts", "speech",]
categories = [ "external-ffi-bindings", "api-bindings",]
repository = "https://github.com/mush42/sonic-sys"
homepage = "https://github.com/mush42/sonic-sys"
readme = "README.md"

[build-dependencies]
cc = "1.0.79"

[build-dependencies.bindgen]
version = "0.59.1"
default-features = false
